♪ Lo‐o‐ove‐ah! ♪

00:06.839 --> 00:09.641
♪ Exciting and new‐ah! ♪

00:09.708 --> 00:12.744
♪ Come aboard ♪

00:12.811 --> 00:15.713
♪ We're expecting you ♪

00:15.779 --> 00:18.916
♪ It's the Love Boat‐ah! ♪

00:18.982 --> 00:22.085
Get the hell away from me.

00:22.152 --> 00:25.021
♪ Love Boat ♪

00:25.087 --> 00:28.024
I'm balling up my fist,
alright?

00:28.090 --> 00:30.025
♪ Set your course
for adventure ♪

00:30.091 --> 00:32.694
♪ Your mind
on a new romance ♪

00:34.729 --> 00:37.398
